nt; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-s=
tyle: solid; background-color: #ccc;">door flew off</a> on a Friday, and th=
e next Monday the stock dropped by 8%, destroying about $12 billion of mark=
et capitalization. There were 177 passengers on the flight, and they each <=
a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/34203294.257394/aHR=
0cHM6Ly9wZW9wbGUuY29tL2FsYXNrYS1haXJsaW5lcy1wYXNzZW5nZXJzLXdoby1zdXJ2aXZlZC=
1taWQtYWlyLWJsb3ctb3V0LWdpdmVuLXVzZDEtNTAwLWJ5LWFpcmxpbmUtODQyNTQ3MSM6fjp0Z=
